data.title: Duchesne Academy
data.text:
Students will come to discover and explore the complexities of the world, historical connections, and current issues.

The area is designed around the maker space principles and encourages creativity, problem solving, and risktaking.

Duchesne Academy offers a multitude of classes in visual and performing arts with numerous opportunities for students to share their gifts and talents through exhibitions and performances.

At Duchesne, sustainability is not just an academic concept, but rather a community-wide commitment to improving the school and the broader world in which we live.
